<http://example.org/req/509#> a owl:Ontology .

<http://example.org/req/509#Competitors> a <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000001>,
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000002>,
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000031>,
        owl:NamedIndividual,
        owl:Thing,
        ns1:InformationContentEntity .

<http://example.org/req/509#Fire_Retardant_Underwear> a <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000001>,
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000002>,
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000031>,
        owl:NamedIndividual,
        owl:Thing,
        ns1:InformationContentEntity .

<http://example.org/req/509#Long_Pants_and_Long_Sleeve_Shirt> a <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000001>,
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000002>,
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000031>,
